        {
            "_id": "5hZxx4bVaqMR8rps",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Heads Will Roll",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The swarm detaches its heads from its bodies and rains them down on its enemies in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] radius within 30 feet. Each head deals falling damage, as if falling from 20 feet up, on any creature it lands on and otherwise takes the damage itself. If a head has a creature within its reach after it falls, it attempts to bite that creature. If any of these bites are critical successes, the head can immediately attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Grapple] the creature.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [
                    {
                        "key": "RollOption",
                        "option": "heads-will-roll",
                        "toggleable": true
                    },
                    {
